{"h367d18e8gab25g46degb5f9gc7cd58d5137c": ["Hold! <i>Hold! Weapons down!</i>", "02025646-347a-4235-aef7-e46b7c94b435", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_EntranceMeeting.html", "9ded21df-9316-582c-2336-f97e77148cd3"], "ha64b308dg0740g4e8cga9c7g76d6867bf8a3": ["Are you bloody <i>mad?</i> We nearly -", "02025646-347a-4235-aef7-e46b7c94b435", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_EntranceMeeting.html", "983d9539-2992-fdbf-ff9d-2a4c2231d62f"], "h8577faa5gf3fag4648g9fd1g8ea24da2545b": ["Never mind. Get up here. I want that gate closed when the goblins arrive.", "02025646-347a-4235-aef7-e46b7c94b435", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_EntranceMeeting.html", "e5567136-887c-f58d-dcb3-f8dac0588016"], "h7268b7c5g85eeg439bg86dbg79227627e751": ["Wait! <i>Wait! Bows down!</i>", "475200ee-cc3c-4dbe-84b1-1820c02ea26a", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_EntranceMeeting.html", "0674b2d0-de94-b281-e7b6-ce81eaf0d91b"], "h70f613edgf769g44a0g96b1g8e38b161ee9a": ["Gods above, we took you for a goblin. Get up here.", "475200ee-cc3c-4dbe-84b1-1820c02ea26a", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_EntranceMeeting.html", "2fb77264-4d4d-795f-a5cc-92034c306ebc"], "hd6728f4dgda75g4fcbg8e13g5bc49f55bee7": ["I want that gate sealed before they arrive - and we need to talk.", "475200ee-cc3c-4dbe-84b1-1820c02ea26a", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_AttackOnDen_EntranceMeeting.html", "68b11438-a96e-0fbf-afbd-d24ef86e7803"]}